Run these Commands from Terminal:

1. git clone https://github.com/neoborn/restifyvote.git
2. cd restifyvote
3. npm install
4. node server.js

Deployment:

1. Ensure that you have OpenShift Account and setup RHC, command line tool for OpenShift
2. Run this command from the terminal:
   rhc create-app <app-name> nodejs-0.10 --from-code https://github.com/neoborn/restifyvote.git
3. The URL will be ready for you to access

[Reference Tutorial](https://www.openshift.com/blogs/day-27-restify-build-correct-rest-web-services-in-nodejs)